                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 2 月 9 日消息，HORI&nbsp;现已经在天猫上架一款适用于&nbsp;PC&nbsp;平台格斗游戏 / 音乐游戏的手台控制器，将于&nbsp;2&nbsp;月 24&nbsp;日首销，<strong>定价为&nbsp;698&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=iqdRf%2Bn8DcClhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOUV9IBA4kmjLbKlr3ReV2ijD6JFPuV48eHum28hqwNh%2Fcwf820GIfdaak2JECJWtA4YIZbF3A8zVkXOdI8VwnS70TcIixZTmmMXh8j4l8nhRjoBQSp5KW1UQS6X%2B6MTmukshqSLEvf%2FK%2BMUwzxYlSKEf4r6%2BEVGe7DpQpEenkiJUL%2BHFZ3%2BbnFiAk6qRGIkpF5IAebCd3jQKLq58KGBdupK588YQeU9YsXT%2FQoCo6pWlxSCwvHEYWuBYbqllJ%2FLsarnJ3AALebIXVW6yqqeGJ%2FI%3D&amp;traceId=213e025817390635492523147e1566&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1739063549@21666f14_0e31_194e843dd8c_b0fd@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i1/2431244162/O1CN01RnVGIQ1gcFRtv7w5Y_!!4611686018427385730-0-item_pic.jpg" title="HORI 推出机械式全按键格斗游戏手台控制器，2 月 24 日 698 元首销" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name"> HORI 机械式全按键手台</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 698 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2236" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/3e204ca9-8115-4305-a7bf-246352e0b416.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzgyLnBuZw==,t_100,g_3,y_15,x_15,a_0/format,f_auto" title="HORI 推出机械式全按键格斗游戏手台控制器，2 月 24 日 698 元首销" width="990" /></p><p>这款手台整体尺寸为&nbsp;30x21x3 mm，便于携带收纳，号称使用了 "HITBOX" 全按键设计，取消了传统的“摇杆加按键”布局，号称“所有输入都采用手感更明确的按键控制”，除了标准的 4 个方向按键和 8+1 个操作按键外，还额外配备有 3 个可自由安装拆卸的扩展按键。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="2333" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/2/9328fad2-44ea-4053-be8b-8764773f027b.png?x-bce-process=image/waterm